    {
      "id": "256260a6-3b21-4c16-b74d-16f8c1438f0a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper proposes the utilization of eye-tracking data to identify learning styles on learners. The authors attempt to use multiple data extrtaction methods and make predictions on a plethora of differetn potential classifiers. ",
